&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About FirstSteps&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The FirstSteps Team is inspired by the belief that every child deserves the opportunity to achieve their fullest potential. To that end, our mission is twofold: to provide the best evidence-based, behavior analytic treatment to our children diagnosed with autism and related learning differences,&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;and&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;to offer a positive, collaborative, and dynamic work experience for our team. We are steadfastly committed&amp;nbsp;to ongoing training and mentorship of our employees, always motivated to support the next generation of clinical leaders in our field and at FirstSteps. Our greatest reward is witnessing the rapid and joyful learning of our little ones and knowing that together, we are creating more happy days for the kids and families we serve.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re hosting a hiring event—come meet us and explore opportunities (open to all!)&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Message &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/firststepsforkids/?hl=en&quot;&gt;@firststepsforkids &lt;/a&gt;on Instagram to RSVP and learn more.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The FirstSteps BCBA Program Director&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;At FirstSteps, we recognize the transformative impact of exceptional clinical leadership. Our Program Directors exemplify these qualities, ensuring that our commitment to clinical excellence and compassionate care remains unwavering.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Overview of the Position &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At FirstSteps, our Program Directors are not only highly skilled behavior analysts but also wonderful leaders and clinicians who bring a unique blend of expertise and person-centered compassionate care to their clinical work. They understand the significance of thorough assessment and develop purpose-driven treatment plans that honor the unique needs and aspirations of each child and caregiver we serve.&amp;nbsp;Collaborating closely with caregivers, educators, therapists, and physicians, our Program Directors establish seamless coordination of care, resulting in the highest level of treatment fidelity and enriched learning environments for all our kids.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Program Directors also play a pivotal role in shaping our renowned clinical curriculum. Their contributions are instrumental in keeping our intervention approaches progressive, evidence-based, and aligned with the latest research and advancements in the field.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leading by example, our Program Directors wholeheartedly embrace the values and mission of FirstSteps. Their dedication to our families and enthusiastic mentorship truly inspires and empowers our entire team to bring their best selves to their work with our kids, ultimately fostering a culture of empathy, understanding, and growth within our organization.&lt;/p&gt;
