&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BCBA Program Director&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A hands-on clinical role for BCBAs who are inspired by kids, understand the importance of purpose-driven, individualized treatment plans, and enjoy mentoring teams.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You didn’t become a BCBA to supervise from a laptop or sign reports for children you rarely see.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most of us entered this field because we wanted to really know our clients, support the teams working with them, and see learning happen in real time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many experienced BCBAs tell us they miss that kind of work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;That’s the kind of work we protect at FirstSteps for Kids.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our BCBAs spend most of their time in the room - observing sessions, coaching RBTs in the moment, and collaborating closely with families and clinical partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you won’t find here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversized caseloads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervision done entirely through telehealth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A culture driven purely by billable hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Instead, &lt;strong&gt;our Program Directors maintain manageable caseloads and a strong center-based presence, allowing you to provide thoughtful supervision and meaningful care.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;$85,000 – $95,000 annual salary&amp;nbsp;(depending on experience)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PLUS:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monetary Signing award&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing Incentive opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Many BCBAs Stay at FirstSteps&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Clinical Home&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Walnut Creek center provides a collaborative environment where clinicians support one another and deliver thoughtful, compassionate ABA.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FirstSteps has long been a &lt;strong&gt;clinician-led organization&lt;/strong&gt;, and maintaining strong clinical integrity continues to guide how we grow and serve families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also believe that our BCBAs doing the work every day should have a meaningful voice in how clinical care evolves.&lt;/p&gt;
